/**
 * The Lotus Flower — SEEDABLE STAGED ARTIFACT (Pre-Genesis)
 *
 * staged: true
 * Composed by /artist on 2026-05-06 per idea-run-11 form recommendation
 * (research/2026-05-06_idea-run-11-lotus-seedable-artifact.md).
 *
 * RELATIONSHIP TO BASELINE:
 *   This file is NEW and DOES NOT replace garden.refreshed.holo.
 *   `garden.refreshed.holo` (A-009 baseline, 2026-05-04) remains the
 *   bloom-state visual-readability reference and is NOT touched here.
 *   `garden.seedable.holo` adds the seedable mathematical-sculpture
 *   spine + Fibonacci-layered petals + deterministic placement on top
 *   of A-009's glow/pulse/pollen vocabulary.
 *
 * FORM (per /idea memo):
 *   Hybrid: golden-angle phyllotaxis spine + Fibonacci-layered petals
 *   (8 inner + 13 middle + 21 outer = 42 petals = 3 program-tiers ×
 *   Fibonacci sequence) + GPUParticleTrait pollen field + @bloom_reactive
 *   driving petal opacity from program-progress signal.
 *
 *   Petal placement is a PURE FUNCTION of LOTUS_GENESIS_SEED. Same seed →
 *   same composition byte-for-byte. Pre-genesis: seed = 0x0000DEAD
 *   (placeholder per project_lotus-genesis-trigger.md). Post-genesis:
 *   seed = first-16-bytes(events.jsonl[0].hash). Staged-vs-live transition
 *   is zero-code-change at composition level — the renderer swaps the seed.
 *
 * DETERMINISM CONTRACT:
 *   - Petal positions: golden-angle 137.50776° spiral, indexed globally
 *     across layers (continuous spiral, not per-layer reset).
 *   - Layer radii: [2.0, 3.4, 4.8] (Fibonacci-derived: 2, 3+1, 5-0.2).
 *   - Layer counts: [8, 13, 21] (Fibonacci sequence F6/F7/F8, mapping
 *     to Programs 1/2/3 by capacity-not-current-content).
 *   - Bloom-state per petal driven by `lotus.api.bloom_state` signal
 *     (already wired in packages/studio/src/lib/brittney/lotus/derive-bloom-state.ts).
 *   - Jitter / particle seed / pollen drift PRNG: SeedHKDF(LOTUS_GENESIS_SEED,
 *     petal_index). Staged seed produces deterministic but visibly muted
 *     palette so genesis-fired version reads as a phase change.
 *
 * I.007 CONSTRAINTS PRESERVED:
 *   - SDF center body deferred to Phase 2 (placeholder mesh until genesis fires).
 *   - GenesisLightColumn declared but `enabled: false` until trigger.
 *   - Genesis chime audio at volume 0.0 until `all_petals_full`.
 *   - Outer-layer (21 petals, Program 3) starts FULLY SEALED — these are
 *     the future capacity slots, named but not paper-bound.
 *
 * FRAME-DRIFT NOTE (W.137):
 *   Pattern-B traits below are marked TODO[trait-binding]. The composition
 *   parses and validates today, but @lotus_root / @lotus_stalk / @lotus_petal
 *   / @lotus_center / @lotus_genesis_trigger / @phyllotaxis / @bloom_reactive
 *   have NO BACKING TRAIT FILES in packages/core/src/traits/. This is the
 *   trait-binding layer of W.137 and the reason this artifact is STAGED.
 *   render_preview will fail until those traits land. validate_holoscript
 *   passes because the parser accepts unbound trait names.
 *
 * @version 1.0.0-staged
 * @format .holo
 * @staged true
 * @cites I.007, W.137, F.014, idea-run-11
 * @traits @lotus_root, @lotus_stalk, @lotus_petal, @lotus_center,
 *         @lotus_genesis_trigger, @phyllotaxis, @bloom_reactive,  (Pattern-B)
 *         @gpu_particle, @glowing, @animated, @spatial_audio       (backed)
 */

composition "Lotus — Seedable Artifact (Pre-Genesis)" {

  metadata {
    title: "The Lotus Flower — Seedable Staged Artifact"
    description: "Deterministic phyllotaxis lotus. 42 petals on a golden-angle spiral, Fibonacci-layered, seeded from LOTUS_GENESIS_SEED. Staged form lives at /lotus pre-genesis; genesis fire swaps the seed and unlocks SDF center + light column."
    version: "1.0.0-staged"
    author: "HoloScript /artist (2026-05-06)"
    staged: true
    seed_hash_placeholder: "0x0000DEAD"
    seed_source_pre_genesis: "env('LOTUS_GENESIS_SEED', '0x0000DEAD')"
    seed_source_post_genesis: "first16bytes(D:/GOLD/anchors/lotus-genesis.json::events[0].hash)"
    cites: ["I.007", "W.137", "F.014", "idea-run-11", "project_lotus-genesis-trigger.md"]
    tags: ["lotus", "seedable", "phyllotaxis", "fibonacci", "staged", "pre-genesis", "16-paper-program"]
  }

  environment {
    skybox: "hdri/dawn_pond.hdr"
    ambient_light: 0.4
    gravity: [0, -9.81, 0]
    shadows: true
  }

